latestPosts.caption:
Langa voni / Pavadai dhavani / Half saree refers to a traditional South Indian attire.

The half saree itself is symbolic, representing the girl’s femininity ( Womanhood )

I personally love half sarees a little more than any other outfit and this particular half saree has been beautifully sewn by @needletechtailors 

Thank you @needletechtailors for this perfect pavadai dhavani I’ve always dreamed of 🤌❤️
